_sText:
This map includes 2 levels: easy and hard. 

There is a boss and some traps on the map. "(p.s)so watch your step"

At the easy level, 2 special items are available for people (gravity and heal). 

On the hard level, there are 2 special items for humans and 3 items for zombies (push, gravity and speed).
If there are any errors write in the comments.
